            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_319gc' title='Col. 319GC &mdash; HL Deb 03 February 2004 vol 656 c319GC' name='column_319gc' href='#column_319gc' rel='bookmark'>319GC</a>
            Earlier we discussed new technologies. In a sense, given the scale on which we envisage this technology, it is new. Therefore, it is important that we consider all the exploitation&#x2014;I did not mean to use that word; I meant to say, "advantages and disadvantages"&#x2014;that it could bring to the countryside. I used the word "exploitation" in error, as that one word caught my eye in Amendment No. 106A.
          </p>
